Localization.Name: Hull C Poster
Localization.Description: Honor an industrial workhorse with this unique and visually stunning poster of the MISC Hull C. Featuring the ship's silhouette set against a colorful swirling spacescape, the poster highlights the Hull C's iconic design by having its spindle extended.
